</title>
<subSubSection id="D051274B6598C01E423B2184000E74AD" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" type="description">
<paragraph id="FC9A447F07924FB7E3460B30E472CE05" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
50-100 cm hoch. Rhizom wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="09ED091132E02FB5E42B7DF6D4A4ABC8" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Holoschoenus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis id="84D42F6659306176FE2E964F0167B981" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. vulgaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1). 
<emphasis id="6ED6B27795B74164F6C67F2713B7B22E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Blattspreiten stets vorhanden; unterste</emphasis>
(spreitenlose) 
<emphasis id="29EDA7FFAA3948B9007630976853D5A1" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
Blattscheiden 1-3 cm lang, gelblich, mit braunem Rand. Die meisten Stengel am Grunde oberhalb der Blattscheiden weniger als 2,5 mm dick. Hochblatt bis 10mal so lang wie der 
<normalizedToken id="5BA7DF249AE9BCA108CF606AD5CC4552" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
. 
<normalizedToken id="7CAEEBEEA6EB2EF308D1310B9C8FFDF7" originalValue="Blütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bluetenstand</normalizedToken>
aus 2-4 kugeligen 
<normalizedToken id="F496322A986548F20C487987F174BB7B" originalValue="Köpfen" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Koepfen</normalizedToken>
.
</emphasis>
Frucht wie bei 
<taxonomicName id="F51474B30C6434BDEBEB57AE4CAE750E" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Holoschoenus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis id="C31F682060001E78A53A1B99483B4781" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. vulgaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 1). - 
<normalizedToken id="BF8ECA5A658EB242D2758210622F9422" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="4C228AA4E1C530810433A1926867D2BF" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="9D38A00A161DAE30A559E408AC8F1598" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="A36E46434AE05B17A182E55D608B8652" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="7C027B8160A034313D2B1587A49F3341" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin. Seeufer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="41C4C3BDEE185C9C6E178AAEE1F35C9A" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="ABCB686A54A773E089CD86970541115A" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Verbreitung.</emphasis>
Nichts bekannt, da meist nicht von 
<taxonomicName id="A253A5B582E1A4624F25D06A0EDE53FF" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Holoschoenus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="vulgaris">
<emphasis id="D57578A2D1FBD14B27432A7A36632F54" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. vulgaris</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
unterschieden: Mediterrangebiet. - Im Gebiet: Im Tessin erloschen (
<normalizedToken id="6C9D0BC487FB3F4CF970D9BB91941BF7" originalValue="Dübi" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Duebi</normalizedToken>
in lit. 1963); angrenzende italienische Gebiete, Comersee, Seen von Varese und Alserio [
<normalizedToken id="18EA12560DF04FF114BD6AEEC767D75A" originalValue="Dübi" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Duebi</normalizedToken>
1953 1960]), in St. Gallen (Buchs) erloschen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="2FDEBBEAD6AF6B7481519FC9D9425556" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">
<emphasis id="F7154D0B47C4014982D8B49675C5C5A7" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">Bemerkungen.</emphasis>
Becherer (1929a) hat 
<taxonomicName id="F4D8D369B39A9BCE3470FD1099BCBEDC" authority="Koch" authorityName="Koch" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Scirpus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="australis">
<emphasis id="ECCDDE8A99145FCEEE0D2D837D188093" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. australis</emphasis>
Koch
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="2B1DA003EA09F4D7922E8362EB04E70A" authority="Rchb." authorityName="Rchb." class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Holoschoenus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="globifer">
<emphasis id="E3BC58B20F68BF86FA5A66EA2D6F1A69" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. globifer</emphasis>
Rchb.
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="B6CC8297BEF28B4377C80D84A5AC3C3B" authority="Nyman" authorityName="Nyman" class="Liliopsida" family="Potamogetonaceae" genus="Potamogeton" kingdom="Plantae" order="Alismatales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="panormitanus">
<emphasis id="DE2FB9247BD03D1BC51B1AF104F95607" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. panormitanus</emphasis>
Nyman
</taxonomicName>
und 
<taxonomicName id="23C0FC2EC877EDB1D5293D79D90D9401" authority="Fritsch" authorityName="Fritsch" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Holoschoenus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="romanus">
<emphasis id="82DF8BE2A595D46DA21947ACCA066738" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. romanus</emphasis>
Fritsch
</taxonomicName>
unter dem Namen 
<taxonomicName id="432F465BF706C2647F73586A784D82C5" authority="Fritsch emend. Becherer" authorityName="Becherer" class="Liliopsida" family="Cyperaceae" genus="Holoschoenus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Poales" pageId="null" pageNumber="411" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="romanus">
<emphasis id="6DB521C2CD0187AA78CB38396255C7D8" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">H. romanus</emphasis>
Fritsch emend. Becherer
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="B8C7180D5D0581FAF63C31329B3C1CAC" originalValue="zusammengefaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">zusammengefasst</normalizedToken>
. Experimentelle Untersuchungen sollten 
<normalizedToken id="6A729BD4AB34BFEE36CE4CFB64C0DABA" originalValue="über" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">ueber</normalizedToken>
die Gliederung der Artengruppe Klarheit schaffen; erst dann 
<normalizedToken id="3C3777C1821A9832307E1295F009F8BD" originalValue="muß" pageId="null" pageNumber="411">muss</normalizedToken>
auch die Nomenklatur diskutiert werden.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
